OL,5, The Islamic police in Nigeria's        
OL,6, northern state of Kano arrested 11     
OL,7, Muslims on Tuesday who were seen eating
OL,8, food during the Ramadan fast.          
OL,10,FKano has a majority Muslim population, 
OL,11,Fwhere an Islamic legal system - Sharia 
OL,12,F- operates alongside secular law.      
OL,14,FThe Islamic police, widely known as    
OL,15,FHisbah, carry out searches of eateries 
OL,16,Fand markets every year during Ramadan. 
OL,18,FThe 10 men and one woman were released 
OL,19,Fafter swearing an oath that they would 
OL,20,Fnot purposely miss a fast again.       
